import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Layout from '../../components/Layout'

/**

**/

const Category = (props) => {
  return(
   <Layout sidebar>
      <Container>
          <Row>
              <Col>
              </Col>
          </Row>
      </Container>
   </Layout>
   )

 }

export default Category
